\pard\plain \fi720\sl288\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Universal language that we all know. Hidden. That it is Discovered.}
\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Sounds fairily, but I hate the idea of universal language. Languages of this world are so variable and different, it makes them unique, wonderful, beautiful and mysterious. And I'm obsessed with learning them. }
