\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 In a good character arc, the MC is shown to be a certain way, wants something, tries and fails to get that thing, gets the thing, pays a price for getting the thing, returns to her original circumstances, and is shown to have changed. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandri is drifting with a spark. Wants to be obliterated. Is obliterated. Is not happy with this. Return to having a Spark.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \~A man goes on a quest, overcomes adversity, reaches his goal, a truth is revealed and the man is changed forever by the revelation.  }}